FBIS3-52490 "drnes003_s_94010" FBIS-NES-94-003 Document Type:Daily Report 5 Jan 1994 Iran Reports on Arrest of Ayatollah Rowhani Denied LD0501151294 Tehran IRNA in English 1449 GMT 5 Jan 94 LD0501151294 Tehran IRNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Qom, Jan. 5, IRNA -- Hojjat ol-Eslam Mohammad 'Ali Rowhani on Wednesday denied a REUTER news despatch alleging that his father Ayatollah Mohammad Rowhani had been arrested. He told IRNA that his father as usual delivered his daily lectures at the theological school today. REUTER in a news despatch today quoted an Iranian dissident Mahdi Haeri as claiming that Ayatollah Rowhani had been arrested and taken to an unknown place by Iranian security agents. The claim of Ayatollah Rowhani's detention was also denied by the commander of a law enforcement headquarters in this holy city.
